Package gobblin.metrics.metric.filter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MetricFilters
    A utility class for working with MetricFilters.
    MetricNameRegexFilter
    Implementation of MetricFilter that takes in a regex, and MetricNameRegexFilter.matches(String, Metric) a Metric if the name of the Metric matches the regex.
    MetricTypeFilter
    Implementation of MetricFilter that takes in a String containing a comma separated list of Metrics.
